---
layout: "base.njk"
title: "Blog"
description: "Découvrez tous les articles de blog de Cédric sur l'entrepreneuriat et le développement d'activité."
locale: "fr"
permalink: "/blog/"
translation: "/en/blog/"
---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16 space-y-12">
  <header class="space-y-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-[#0f172a]">Blog</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[#1f1f1f]/80">Articles de Cédric sur l'entrepreneuriat et le développement d'une activité fluide, unique et vous correspondant</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#1f1f1f]/60">
      <a href="{{ '/feed.xml' | relativeUrl }}" type="application/rss+xml" class="text-[#0A6BCE] hover:underline inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="S'abonner au flux RSS">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M5 3a1 1 0 000 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10a1 1 0 102 0C17 8.373 11.627 3 5 3z"></path>
          <path d="M4 9a1 1 0 011-1 7 7 0 017 7 1 1 0 11-2 0A5 5 0 005 11a1 1 0 01-1-1z"></path>
          <path d="M4 13a1 1 0 011-1 3 3 0 013 3 1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 00-1-1 1 1 0 01-1-1z"></path>
        </svg>
        Flux RSS
      </a>
    </p>
  </header>

  <article class="h-feed max-w-none space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      {% for post in collections.blogPostsFr %}
        <div class="h-entry section-card p-6 bg-white hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h2 class="p-name text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0f172a] mb-3">
            <a href="{{ post.url | relativeUrl }}" class="u-url text-[#0A6BCE] hover:underline">
              {{ post.data.title }}
            </a>
          </h2>
          {% if post.data.description %}
            <p class="p-summary text-lg text-[#1f1f1f]/80 mb-3 line-clamp-3">
              {{ post.data.description | truncate(160) }}
            </p>
          {% endif %}
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-[#1f1f1f]/60">
            {% if post.data.date %}
              <time class="dt-published" datetime="{{ post.data.date }}">{{ post.data.date | date('d MMMM yyyy', 'fr') }}</time>
            {% endif %}
            <a href="{{ post.url | relativeUrl }}" class="u-url text-[#0A6BCE] hover:underline font-semibold">
              Lire l'article →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
